name: Tic Tac Toe 2023
description:
Long time ago, before Wednesday was a hit tv show, I tried developing my first game which was tic tac toe. I failed horribly and here I am back with a vengeance and the Unity game engine. :)

Tic Tac Toe made with the Unity game engine.

Supports only 2 player (play with a friend or by yourself (like me)).
